---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Article',
  headline: 'Originality Ai vs Copyleaks: Which Detector is Better? [2026 Comparison]',
  description: 'Originality Ai vs Copyleaks detailed comparison. Features, pricing, accuracy, and user reviews. Find the best AI content detection tool for your needs.',
  datePublished: '2026-03-11',
  dateModified: '2026-03-11',
};

const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Is Originality Ai better than Copyleaks?',
    answer: 'Both Originality Ai and Copyleaks are popular AI content detection tools. Originality Ai is known for its accuracy and speed, while Copyleaks excels in ease of use. The best choice depends on your specific needs and budget.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Which is more accurate: Originality Ai or Copyleaks?',
    answer: 'Accuracy varies by use case. Originality Ai typically performs better with academic content, while Copyleaks shows strength in detecting marketing copy. Test both with your specific content type for best results.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What is the pricing difference between Originality Ai and Copyleaks?',
    answer: 'Originality Ai offers both free and premium plans starting around $10-20/month. Copyleaks has a similar pricing structure. Check each tool\'s current pricing for the most accurate information.',
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Originality Ai vs Copyleaks: Which Detector is Better? [2026 Comparison]"
  description="Originality Ai vs Copyleaks detailed comparison. Features, pricing, accuracy, and user reviews. Find the best AI content detection tool for your needs."
  schema={schema}
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Originality Ai vs Copyleaks: Which Detector is Better? [2026 Comparison]</h1>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">Originality Ai vs Copyleaks detailed comparison. Features, pricing, accuracy, and user reviews. Find the best AI content detection tool for your needs.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Originality Ai</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Originality Ai is a leading AI content detection tool known for its high accuracy rates and comprehensive analysis.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>✅ High accuracy</li>
          <li>✅ Fast processing</li>
          <li>✅ Detailed reports</li>
          <li>✅ API access available</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Copyleaks</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Copyleaks offers reliable detection with user-friendly interface.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>✅ Easy to use</li>
          <li>✅ Affordable pricing</li>
          <li>✅ Good accuracy</li>
          <li>✅ Customer support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">Key Differences</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="border p-3 text-left">Feature</th>
            <th class="border p-3 text-left">Originality Ai</th>
            <th class="border p-3 text-left">Copyleaks</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Accuracy</td>
            <td class="border p-3">High (95%+)</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Very Good (90%+)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Speed</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Fast</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Very Fast</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Pricing</td>
            <td class="border p-3">$10-50/mo</td>
            <td class="border p-3">$10-40/mo</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border p-3">Free Plan</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Yes</td>
            <td class="border p-3">Yes</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      {faqs.map(faq => (
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{faq.question}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">{faq.answer}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Conclusion</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
      Both Originality Ai and Copyleaks are excellent AI content detection tools. Your choice should depend on your specific requirements, budget, and use case. Try both free plans before committing to a subscription.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
